WEBVTT

00:00.099 --> 00:02.363
Consisting of just snowlike shaved ice...

00:02.445 --> 00:04.996
...topped with condensed milk, sweet red beans and tteok,...

00:05.181 --> 00:07.692
...the original patbingsu really hits the spot.

00:07.825 --> 00:12.496
The one place that holds the secret to the best patbingsu is Meal Top,...

00:12.667 --> 00:14.979
...located in Apgujeong's Hyundai Department Store.

00:15.108 --> 00:18.545
First opened in 1985, Meal Top's legendary patbingsu...

00:18.641 --> 00:20.572
...gained recognition all throughout Seoul...

00:20.661 --> 00:22.815
...as the best of the best of the best of the best.

00:22.935 --> 00:23.697
How good, you ask?

00:23.881 --> 00:26.405
No matter the time of day, the line is so long...

00:26.484 --> 00:29.174
...that you have to pull a number from a machine to be seated.

